_sText: So this is my 3rd real map and ends the trilogy of CS Source maps i have created. Everything in this, like on my other maps too, have been done from scratch. I have not edited any existing maps or anything, this is all from my own head. So In this map, i wanted to try out another scenario. 1 close bombsite and 1 more far away. Its all about the teamwork which team will win. There are enough routes to avoid bottleneck fights and it is fully balanced for both teams! This map is on cycle at server: 89.166.50.111:27025 I created this during 2 months of time. This is the best optimized map i have done since the start to the end. It compiles on normal only in 19 minutes which i consider a good result! I left HDR off because it cutted -100fps off straight on, even if i really tried to optimize it to the map. It did that even if it wouldnt be on at players PC but the map had support for HDR. Weird stuff, i know but map looks fine without it too! Playability over eyecandy, thats my motto. Check out all my other maps from http://www.ics-base.net/css_maps
